<div class="row">
  The following is the configuration that works for most. Feel free to change . You can change the settings anytime in the future by clicking on ### icon on top right.
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h3>Sentiment Analysis</h3>
    <p>Your emails are run through a sentiment analysis algorithm which can detect any anger, dissatisfaction and quantify them for you to prioritize your emails.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <br/><br/><p> Sentiment weight: <span id="sentimentVal">3</span></p><br/>
  <input id="sentiment" type="text" data-slider-min="1" data-slider-max="5" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="3"/&t>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h3>Length of email</h3>
    <p>Your emails are run through a sentiment analysis algorithm which can detect any anger, dissatisfaction and quantify them for you to prioritize your emails.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <br/><br/><p> Email length weight: <span id="lengthVal">3</span></p><br/>
  <input id="length" type="text" data-slider-min="1" data-slider-max="5" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="3"/&t>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-7">
    <h3>No Reply Streak</h3>
    <p>Your emails are run through a sentiment analysis algorithm which can detect any anger, dissatisfaction and quantify them for you to prioritize your emails.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-5">
    <br/><br/><p> Streak weight: <span id="streakVal">3</span></p><br/>
  <input id="streak" type="text" data-slider-min="1" data-slider-max="5" data-slider-step="1" data-slider-value="3"/&t>
